---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bidwell Capital - Strategic Wealth Building Through Real Assets">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-up fade-up-1">Bidwell Capital</span>
      <h1 class="fade-up fade-up-2">Build generational wealth<br/>through real assets</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub fade-up fade-up-3">We only bring you opportunities we personally believe in, with clear, disciplined projections. We manage with integrity to ensure your confidence in every step we take.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions fade-up fade-up-4">
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">How We Invest</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Start a Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="stat-card card fade-up fade-up-2">
          <span class="stat-value">$10M+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Investor Capital Raised</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card card fade-up fade-up-3">
          <span class="stat-value">3</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Active Strategies</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card card fade-up fade-up-4">
          <span class="stat-value">96</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Investors</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="disclaimer" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">Past performance is not indicative of future results. All investments carry risk, including loss of principal.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Why Bidwell Capital</span>
      <h2>Built different</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">We are not a Wall Street firm. We are operators and investors building alongside you for the long term.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Real assets only</h3>
          <p>We understand the layers of wealth and focus on primary and secondary wealth. Commercial real estate credit, multifamily real estate, and energy. Things you can see, touch, and value. No crypto, no speculative bets, no financial engineering.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Long-term partners, not salespeople</h3>
          <p>We are young managing partners building and managing assets for decades, not starting a second career in our 50s. This is not a transaction or a get-rich-quick scheme. We are building long-term wealth, growing a team around a mission we believe in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Disciplined underwriting you can trust</h3>
          <p>Returns are a premium on risk, and we take that seriously. We leverage deep personal connections with industry leaders and constantly stress-test every investment thesis before committing capital. Our underwriting is transparent, simple, and conservative. We minimize and educate on spreadsheet magic.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center;">
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More About Our Strategy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who We Work With -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="who-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Who We Work With</span>
          <h2>Busy builders who want their money working as hard as they do</h2>
          <p>Our investors are typically entrepreneurial, high-net-worth individuals between 35 and 65. They value freedom, they are time constrained, and they are not looking to become full-time real estate professionals. They want to build freedom for themselves and their families.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Many of them have tax problems they need solved. Most want more cashflow. All of them want to build real, lasting wealth without having to manage it day to day.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">If that sounds like you, we should talk.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Conversation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="who-values">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Cashflow</h3>
            <p>Strong, regular income from assets that pay you to own them.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <h3>Tax benefits</h3>
            <p>Real deductions that put money back in your pocket.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <h3>Freedom</h3>
            <p>True wealth transcends finances. It begins with freedom. Hear more on the <a href="https://www.wealthindependencepod.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--accent);">Wealth Independence Podcast</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Investor Club -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="club-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Investor Club</span>
          <h2>Get access before the public</h2>
          <p>Bidwell Capital offerings are available exclusively through our Investor Club under SEC Regulation D, Rule 506(b). Our deals are not publicly advertised. They are shared directly with qualified members.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Club members get first look at new deals, access to our Deal Observer program to follow active positions in real time, monthly updates on portfolio performance, and direct access to our team.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Membership is free. We just need to verify that you qualify as an accredited investor through a short introductory call.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <a href="/contact#book" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Qualification Call</a>
          </div>
          <p class="disclaimer" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Under SEC Rule 506(b), securities may only be offered to accredited investors and up to 35 sophisticated non-accredited investors. No general solicitation or advertising is permitted.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="club-perks">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Early deal access</h3>
            <p>See new opportunities before they close. Many of our deals fill quickly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <h3>Deal Observer</h3>
            <p>Not ready to invest? Watch how our active deals perform with real monthly updates. No commitment required.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <h3>Direct communication</h3>
            <p>No gatekeepers. You get direct access to our team and transparent reporting on every deal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Promise -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; max-width: 42rem;">
      <span class="section-label">Our Promise</span>
      <h2>Integrity in every step</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">We will only bring you opportunities we personally believe in, with clear, disciplined projections. We will manage with integrity to ensure your confidence in every step we take. Together we will build generational wealth.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
      padding: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 55ch;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .who-grid, .club-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .who-grid h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  }

  .who-values h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.375rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .who-grid, .club-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }
</style>
